UUssaaggee
       The  system-supplied  Poll  file  only   contains   sample
       entries.   Unless  polling  is  required, the file usually
       does not need to be modified.

EExxaammpplleess
       The Poll file entry: eagle0 4 8 12 16 20  polls  the  com-
       puter eagle every four hours.

